browse-sqlite3 1.0 (2026-02-21)
--------------------------------
- Initial release
- Three-view TUI: table list, row browser, field editor
- Vi-style navigation, readline-style inline editing
- Turbo Pascal IDE color scheme via exact CGA palette values
- Multi-column sort with persistent ordering
- Structured find/filter with SQL WHERE generation
- Per-column find dialog with AND/OR toggles
- Safety mode for destructive operations
- External editor and pager integration
- East Asian wide-character display support
- Optional C extension for Unicode display-width acceleration
- bs3 command alias
